// [RADAR] cfg_sender: Automatically sends ISK_6m_default.cfg
// to the IWR6843 UART RX port after reset is released.
//
// IWR6843 has two UART ports:
//   - Data port (sensorStop frame output): connected to radar_uart_rxd (JA1)
//   - Config port (accepts .cfg commands): connected to radar_cfg_tx (JB3)
//
// The cfg_sender sends the complete .cfg file contents byte-by-byte
// at 115200 baud immediately when soc_reset deasserts. After the cfg
// is sent it idles — no firmware intervention needed.
// ================================================================
